---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="How It Works | Auto Video">
  <h1>How It Works</h1>
  <section class="grid">
    <article class="card"><h3>1. Describe your idea</h3><p>Provide one prompt with goal, audience, and tone.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>2. AI writes the narrative</h3><p>We auto-build script blocks and visual scene direction.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>3. Assemble scenes</h3><p>Motion style, text overlays, and transitions are selected automatically.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>4. Add voice-over</h3><p>Choose a speaking style and pacing for your target platform.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>5. Export and publish</h3><p>Download your video or hand off to your content team.</p></article>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
